General.Name: Scibase AB
General.Description: SciBase Holding AB (publ), a medical technology company, develops and sells instruments for the detection of skin cancer and other skin conditions in Europe and internationally. The company operates through Skin Cancer and Skin Barrier Assessment segments. Its products include Nevisense and Nevisense Go point of care platforms that addresses in the areas of melanoma detection, non-melanoma skin cancer detection, and skin barrier assessment. SciBase Holding AB (publ) was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Sundbyberg, Sweden.
